          <div class="faq-answer">GPTZero is an AI content detector. Paste text in and it predicts whether the words came from a human, an AI model (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Llama, Mistral), or a mix. It highlights AI-likely sentences and gives a probability score.</div>
