        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How accurate is GPTZero?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">85-95% accurate on unedited AI text. Drops to 60-75% on AI content that has been edited by a human. False positives on human-written text happen in 5-15% of cases.</div>
